{"tid":1088554,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"用幾首歌或者歌詞去講下自己嘅故事同感受","createTime":"2019-04-02T06:41:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-05T08:09:45.000Z","uid":187037,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"2b6961474556d132865cb52fec471c527504b13a","tid":1088554,"uid":187037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T06:41:54.000Z","msg":"我先 順序<br />\n七百年後 陳奕迅<br />\n時差 Kolor<br />\n無人之境 陳奕迅<br />\n三十日 側田<br />\n人來人往 陳奕迅<br />\n綿綿 陳奕迅<br />\n火花不等人 劉浩龍<br />\n情永落 側田<br />\n百年樹木 張敬軒<br />\n有冇人明白我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果你知道我係邊個，唔好起我底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"957680b42f18a85cd099a572672fd690e8d24911","tid":1088554,"uid":8033,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T07:17:55.000Z","msg":"怎麼這世界好像越來越陌生了 <br />\n我知道我不該停下腳步 <br />\n對你 記得我承諾過 <br />\n<br />\n又過了多少不起眼的日子 <br />\n又吃了多少食之無味的晚餐 <br />\n而寂寞的冬天仍下著雨 <br />\n夜晚的城市也依舊孤單 <br />\n<br />\n也不是非要懷念什麼吧 <br />\n只是遺失的歲月有一些感傷"},{"pid":"76495d22b16e8960493d7731ee69e8939566410f","tid":1088554,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T07:19:54.000Z","msg":"我知你係邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"182ea82f6bbdc9e58fefa0207b1973435387e995","tid":1088554,"uid":187037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76495d22b16e8960493d7731ee69e8939566410f","tid":1088554,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T07:19:54.000Z","msg":"我知你係邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-02T07:29:41.000Z","msg":"真的嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d079c128784f341b56390427ab7be9d43cde9bed","tid":1088554,"uid":187037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":